{"tid":1428054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集中討論] 如何回應是日狗記招","createTime":"2019-08-07T08:40:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T08:44:44.000Z","uid":79161,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"488f7c91a04453c016ee5394d9550f7314686eac","tid":1428054,"uid":79161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:40:38.000Z","msg":"教育藍絲嘅論點<br />\n<br />\n(1) 警察造假, 射向黑色吸熱點<br />\n(2) 警察造假, 近距離射<br />\n(3) 警察造假, 長時間聚焦同一點<br />\n(4) 警察造假, 會長冇買咁強W嘅雷射筆<br />\n(5) 警察使用緊嘅係軍火, 大量案例造成大量死亡、瞎眼、永久殘廢, 相反雷射筆不值一提<br />\n(6) 警察高空射擊, 非法掉炮仗<br />\n<br />\n結論：黑警濫用武力 &gt;&gt; 市民手無搏雞之力<br />\n<br />\n諗到再講<br />\n剩係係連登圍爐講係冇用<br />\n唔該文宣一齊整圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傳出去whatsapp we7俾藍絲睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db73a3f454c3e9b60fc038ff0145a92c9e8ff369","tid":1428054,"uid":268537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:42:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"acc3e25dcf4a082d4ab41c2e2e22632eff2e0e6b","tid":1428054,"uid":79161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:44:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8408da5feaff522b9421fc66e1c1d81efa3a8898","tid":1428054,"uid":79161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:44:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e87734122b21b9cf4cddf376f3f7213e443cdd0","tid":1428054,"uid":79161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:44:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}